-------------------------------------------------------------------------
x_macro.sh
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
Simple analysis macros compatible with 'runTest' command line interface.
Macros are executed via 'x_macro.sh' script.
It uses (almost) the same commands as 'runTests' which start macros
corresponding to the measurement type.
Run './x_macro.sh --help' for more information.
First parameter is the path to the datafile.

e.g. ./x_macro.sh GEN /path/to/SouceScan_*_*.dat 
     plots source hit map
e.g. ./x_macro.sh THRESHOLD /path/to/ThresholdScan_*_*.sh
     plots scan results and calculates thresholds

-------------------------------------------------------------------------
monitoring/
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
Simple event by event monitoring.
Execute by:
./x_mon.sh /path/to/RawHits_*_*.dat
